    <para id="para-00070"><emphasis effect="bold">Step 1:</emphasis> Determine whether any candidate received a majority. There were 21 ballots. Fifty percent of 21 is <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline"><mrow><mn>0.50</mn><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mn>21</mn><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo>=</mo><mn>10.5</mn></mrow></math>. A majority is 11.</para>
